OL,3,CRoyal Navy warship heads to Middle
OL,4,CEast for potential Strait of Hormuz
OL,5,Cmission
OL,7,FA Royal Navy warship is being sent to
OL,8,Fthe Middle East to be ready to join an
OL,9,Finternational mission to safeguard
OL,10,Fshipping in the Strait of Hormuz.
OL,12,FType 45 destroyer HMS Dragon will "pre-
OL,13,Fposition" in the region, ready to join
OL,14,Fthe UK and French-led initiative once
OL,15,Fhostilities cease between Iran and US-
OL,16,FIsraeli forces.
OL,26,@tD@cOUuD@IO]
