PN,31702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1778432758
OL,3,CRoyal Navy warship heads to Middle
OL,4,CEast for potential Strait of Hormuz
OL,5,Cmission
OL,7,FA fragile ceasefire remains in place,
OL,8,Falthough attacks on Friday saw US
OL,9,Fforces hit two Iranian tankers that
OL,10,Fwere trying to breach the blockade
OL,11,Fimposed by Donald Trump.
OL,13,FThe proposed mission championed by Sir
OL,14,FKeir Starmer and French President
OL,15,FEmmanuel Macron would involve a
OL,16,Fcoalition of nations willing to ensure
OL,17,Ffreedom of navigation in the strait, a
OL,18,Fvital route for global oil and gas
OL,19,Fsupplies along with other goods
OL,20,Fincluding fertiliser.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/5
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
