FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1778432758
OL,3,CRoyal Navy warship heads to Middle
OL,4,CEast for potential Strait of Hormuz
OL,5,Cmission
OL,7,FA Ministry of Defence spokesman said:
OL,8,F"We can confirm that HMS Dragon will
OL,9,Fdeploy to the Middle East to pre-
OL,10,Fposition ahead of any future
OL,11,Fmultinational mission to protect
OL,12,Finternational shipping when conditions
OL,13,Fallow them to transit the Strait of
OL,14,FHormuz.
OL,16,F"The pre-positioning of HMS Dragon is
OL,17,Fpart of prudent planning that will
OL,18,Fensure that the UK is ready, as part
OL,19,Fof a multinational coalition jointly
OL,20,Fled by the UK and France, to secure
OL,21,Fthe strait, when conditions allow."
OL,26,@pD@AOUxD@AOU}D@cO]
