PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1778432758
OL,3,CRoyal Navy warship heads to Middle
OL,4,CEast for potential Strait of Hormuz
OL,5,Cmission
OL,7,FThe decision to move HMS Dragon from
OL,8,Fthe eastern Mediterranean, where it
OL,9,Fhad been defending British bases on
OL,10,FCyprus, will allow the destroyer to
OL,11,Fcontribute immediately should the
OL,12,Fdefensive mission in the strait be
OL,13,Flaunched.
